      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "**✨ Major UI Refresh & Better Clarity**\r\nThis update completely overhauls the export experience to make it feel more \"at home\" in Obsidian, while making it much easier to see exactly what you’re exporting.\r\n\r\n**🎨 A Fresh New Look**\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1304\" height=\"1074\" alt=\"demo\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/24bea7a1-33ec-42de-95c7-2cb72aa55252\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n- Modern Export Dialog: The export window has been redesigned from the ground up with better spacing, typography, and icons for a truly premium, native Obsidian feel.\r\n- Interactive File Tree: Instead of a simple flat list, you can now see your files in a proper link structure, making it much easier to understand the relationships between your notes.\r\n- Clearer Exclusions: replaced cluttered \"Filtered\" labels with intuitive visual cues. Any files or folders being ignored (based on your settings) now show up with a clean red strikethrough—no guesswork required.\r\n\r\n**🔡 Simpler & Clearer**\r\n\r\n- Renamed for Clarity: renamed the main command to `Export note & related files`. It’s simpler, more descriptive, and tells you exactly what it does.\r\n- Updated Documentation: The README and plugin guides have been refreshed to match these new names and features.\r\n\r\nThis plugin has reached maturity with all planned features implemented and thus the version has been bumped from `0.1.14` to `0.2.0`.\r\n",
      "downloadCount": 109,
      "draft": false,
      "name": "0.2.0",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2025-12-23T07:02:30Z",
      "tag": "0.2.0"
    },
