          "size": 356
        }
      ],
      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "**New Features**\r\n- Markdown Link Support: Added support for standard markdown links `[text](path)`, expanding beyond the previous wikilink-only support.\r\n- Canvas Support:\r\n    - Full tracking and exporting for files linked inside Canvas files.\r\n    - Supports both file nodes and links within text nodes.\r\n- Enhanced Link Resolution: Now supports all 3 Obsidian link resolution modes:\r\n    - Shortest path when available.\r\n    - Relative path from current file.\r\n    - Absolute path from vault root.\r\n- Mixed Link Types: Seamlessly handles documents containing both markdown links and wikilinks.\r\n\r\n**Engineering**\r\n- Added comprehensive unit tests to ensure reliability of link resolution and export logic.\r\n- Bug Fixes\r\n- Closes #2\r\n- Closes #7",
      "downloadCount": 100,
      "draft": false,
