      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "Implemented comprehensive header hierarchy support which enables users to organize exported files according to the header structure of the source note, creating a semantic folder structure that mirrors the document's outline.\r\n\r\nContributed by @oscaromsn\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n* feat: add header hierarchy support for linked note exports by @oscaromsn in https://github.com/the-c0d3r/obsidian-linked-note-exporter/pull/6\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @oscaromsn made their first contribution in https://github.com/the-c0d3r/obsidian-linked-note-exporter/pull/6 : thanks a lot\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/the-c0d3r/obsidian-linked-note-exporter/compare/0.1.12...0.1.13",
